WEBVTT

00:00:28.968 --> 00:00:30.127
u njezine rogove,

00:00:30.151 --> 00:00:31.312
njezine mišiće,

00:00:31.336 --> 00:00:32.717
sve me to plašilo.

00:00:32.741 --> 00:00:37.114
Nisam znao je li ona čudovište ili heroj.

00:00:37.138 --> 00:00:40.360
Odlučio sam pitati tadašnjeg "Google-a":

00:00:40.384 --> 00:00:41.664
"Mama! Mama!"

00:00:41.688 --> 00:00:43.584
(Smijeh)

00:00:43.608 --> 00:00:48.049
Majka mi je objasnila da je
Zelena Dama zapravo Kip slobode

00:00:48.073 --> 00:00:50.344
te da je mahala imigrantima na ulasku.

00:00:50.368 --> 00:00:54.663
Dio njezinog objašnjenja
koji moja mlada glava nije shvatila

00:00:54.687 --> 00:00:57.322
je činjenica da, prema njezinim riječima,

00:00:57.346 --> 00:00:59.379
davno prije nas,

00:00:59.403 --> 00:01:02.555
Zelena je dama bila zapravo smeđa,